/* import specific icons */
import { 
    faUserSecret , 
    faBell , 
    faSearch , 
    faInbox ,
    faDashboard ,
    faContactBook ,
    faFile ,
    faRobot ,
    faUserFriends ,
    faTimeline ,
    faCalendar ,
    faBook ,
    faChartArea ,
    faUnlock ,
    faBookAtlas ,
    faAr

} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'
/* import the fontawesome core */
import { library } from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core'

/* add icons to the library */
library.add(
    faUserSecret , 
    faBell , 
    faSearch , 
    faInbox ,
    faDashboard ,
    faContactBook ,
    faFile ,
    faRobot ,
    faUserFriends ,
    faTimeline ,
    faCalendar ,
    faBook ,
    faChartArea ,
    faUnlock ,
    faBookAtlas
    )
